snippet.title: Wizeline Data Engineering featuring Tania Reyes
snippet.description:
Tania discovered her interest in Big Data while working at Wizeline and took Wizeline Academy courses to skill up and join the data team.

Now, she works on internal and external big data projects, helping people gain insights from their data. Watch the full story! 

Want to join our Data team? We’re always hiring. Visit wizeline.com/careers and search our open roles.
